<BaseLayout lang="en" title="Tolantongo Thermal Waters — Natural 36°C Springs in Hidalgo, Mexico" description="Tolantongo thermal waters: natural 36°C geothermal springs, rich in carbonates and minerals. Grottoes, pools and thermal river in Cardonal, Hidalgo." canonical="/en/thermal-waters/" schema={schema}>
